# Project 04 — YouTube Outlier Finder

---

## 📌 Overview

Automated YouTube trend monitoring system built with n8n.

The workflow continuously scans multiple YouTube niches, analyzes newly published videos, identifies high-performing outliers based on engagement metrics and automatically delivers the most promising content directly to Telegram.

---

## 🎯 Goal

Automatically discover viral YouTube videos before they become mainstream, allowing creators, researchers and content teams to identify successful content ideas and emerging trends with minimal manual effort.

---

## ⚙️ Features

- Scheduled automatic execution
- Multi-niche YouTube search
- YouTube Data API integration
- Automatic video statistics collection
